[9.222, "o", "\r\n  1. PRD R-3 (auth) specifies API-key only; ADR-002 adopts OAuth \u2014 contradiction at authority level.\r\n  2. FEAT-001 still references API-key flow; design has shifted.\r\n  3. No security-architecture artifact exists; OAuth introduces session/token lifecycle that needs one.\r\n"]
